1.0.0 2026-05-02
    - Initial release
    - Three-column contacts page (Tools menu) with live HTMX search and filters
    - Personal contact markings with private notes
    - Group contact markings per RT group
    - Contact detail pane: profile photo, address, phone, recent tickets, held assets, updated articles
    - Inline user creation with all fields and photo upload (requires AdminUsers right)
    - Inline user editing directly in the detail pane
    - Create ticket button pre-fills requestor from selected contact
    - Manage Contacts page (user menu): list, search, add, remove, import, export
    - CSV export (personal contacts or all contacts) and CSV import
    - Contact markings stored in new contact_markings table (auto-created)
    - Permissions: SeeContacts, ManagePersonalContacts, ManageGroupContacts, AdminContacts
    - Bootstrap 5.3 / dark-mode aware via var(--bs-*) CSS variables
    - HTMX fragment pattern with hx-select (no inherit=>undef, session intact)
    - Profile photos via RT's native /Helpers/UserImage/ endpoint
